request.description:
### Register User

This endpoint allows the user to register with the application.

#### Request Body

- name (text, required): The name of the user.

- email (text, required): The email address of the user.

- password (text, required): The password for the user account.

- password_confirmation (text, required): Confirmation of the password.

- app (text, required): The application for which the user is registering.

- role (text, required): The role of the user.


#### **Response**

``` json
{
    "status": "201 Created",
    "message": "Registration successful"
}
 ```

#### Response (JSON Schema)

``` json
{
    "type": "object",
    "properties": {
        "status": {
            "type": "string"
        },
        "message": {
            "type": "string"
        }
    }
}

 ```

