request.description:
### Update User Information

This endpoint is used to update the user information such as first name, last name, email, phone, parent's email, and parent's phone.

#### Request Body

- Type: JSON

    - `first_name`: (string) The first name of the user.

    - `last_name`: (string) The last name of the user.

    - `email`: (string) The email address of the user.

    - `phone`: (string) The phone number of the user.

    - `parent_email`: (string) The email address of the user's parent.

    - `parent_phone`: (string) The phone number of the user's parent.


Example request body:

``` json
{
    "first_name": "John",
    "last_name": "Doe",
    "email": "johndoe@maildrop.cc",
    "phone": "+1234567890",
    "parent_email": "parent@example.com",
    "parent_phone": "+9876543210"
}

 ```

#### Response

- Status: 200

- Content-Type: application/json


Example response body (JSON schema):

``` json
{
    "type": "object",
    "properties": {
        "status": {
            "type": "string"
        },
        "message": {
            "type": "string"
        },
        "data": {
            "type": "object",
            "properties": {
                "id": {
                    "type": "integer"
                },
                "name": {
                    "type": "string"
                },
                "email": {
                    "type": "string"
                },
                "email_verified_at": {
                    "type": ["string", "null"]
                },
                "created_at": {
                    "type": "string"
                },
                "updated_at": {
                    "type": "string"
                },
                "role": {
                    "type": "string"
                },
                "profile": {
                    "type": "object",
                    "properties": {
                        "user_id": {
                            "type": "integer"
                        },
                        "phone": {
                            "type": "string"
                        },
                        "parent_email": {
                            "type": "string"
                        },
                        "parent_phone": {
                            "type": "string"
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    }
}

 ```

